You can download this release from [http://www.openttd.org/download-stable/0.5.0 openttd.org].

==New Features==
* General fixes and improvements to TTDPatch's newgrf format, most noticable are newstations, newsounds, more callbacks and I18n.
* In game NewGRF window.
* Gradual (un)loading of vehicles.
* Allow over-building of compatible railtypes.
* Measurement tool.
* Change the original date format to be based on the year 0. Highest date is the year 5.000.000AC
* Heightmaps support.
* New terrain generator.
* Allow building rails, roads on steep slopes.
* Add four new [[en/Manual/Airports]].
* New pathfinder, [[en/Archive/Manual/Yet Another Pathfinder]].
* Support for electric [[en/Manual/Base Set/Railways]] as a seperate tracktype.
* Add [[en/Archive/Manual/Company Colours|2cc]] (two company colours) livery schemes.

